InventoryItems.Name: Bubble Fun tennis
InventoryItems.Description: Bubbles, tennis, solution, and loads of fun!

InventoryItems.Name: Bubble fun stars and pipes
InventoryItems.Description: Bubble Fun Play Set This bubble fun play set comes with an assortment of bubble makers along with a bottle of bubble solution and a solution tray. There's about 3 ounces of solution in a recloseable bottle that has ingredients on it's label. Other than the standard bubble wand, there are racquets, different styles of blow pipes, and shaped wands like circle, heart, and star. Assortments come in brilliant neon colors. The set comes in blister card package. Colors may vary. Not recommended for children under 3.
